  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Send 120 Pygmies Children to School in Cameroon</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Marginalized, stigmatized, rejected by the by the surrounding Bantu population,the Pygmies have no legal recognition,this project will insure the care of 120 Pygmies children and youth (tuition fees, uniforms, clothing),provide appropriate materials for different levels of education: preschool, elementary and secondary - (school supplies, textbooks, computers),to benefit from medical follow-up (purchase of essential medicines),to have a healthy diet (Creation of an agro-pastoral farm).</narrative>
  </description>
